{"TopicId":148558,"ForumId":25,"TopicTitle":"[BDA] [1.1.3] Airborne Heavy Weapons Platform Challenge- Battles Begin Soon","CreatedByName":"njmksr","CreatedById":114236,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-24T17:19:57Z","PageNum":3,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"drtricky","CreatedById":154647,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-01T18:30:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222782616\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022148558\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221475335716\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022114236\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022njmksr\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, njmksr said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/154647-drtricky/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022154647\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/154647-drtricky/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@drtricky\u003C/a\u003E, are you willing to host the battles?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf I had\u00A0the free time I would.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn addition, the videos would be\u00A0glorified powerpoint slide shows. When I ran the Liberator against my Titan, I was getting 5 FPS, and I know a screen capture program would reduce that even further.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-10-01T18:47:06Z\u0022 title=\u002210/01/2016 06:47  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 1, 2016\u003C/time