ods shown on the KerbalX page, as well as TCA and KJR. It should work then.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kubas_inko","CreatedById":169457,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-02T20:48:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nwhere can i get this?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022aaaaaa.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022https://s18.postimg.org/h8afdyxg9/aaaaaa.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"njmksr","CreatedById":114236,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-02T20:49:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHuh. That seems to be OPT. You have OPT, right?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kubas_inko","CreatedById":169457,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-02T21:49:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222784339\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022148558\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221475441392\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022114236\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022njmksr\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n59 minutes ago, njmksr said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHuh. That seems to be OPT. You have OPT, right?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nyes, I have\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"drtricky","CreatedById":154647,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-02T21:57:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd this is the part where I bring a beach chair and lay back while\u00A0sipping a nice, tall glass of stock parts, watching you two run around figuring out why your planes won\u0027t work.\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan c